CustomField.formula: LPAD(TEXT(MONTH(DATEVALUE(CreatedDate + (1/24)))), 2, "0") + "/" + LPAD(TEXT(DAY(DATEVALUE(CreatedDate + (1/24)))), 2, "0") + "/" + RIGHT(TEXT(YEAR(DATEVALUE(CreatedDate + (1/24)))),2) + " " + LPAD(TEXT(HOUR(TIMEVALUE(CreatedDate + (1/24)))), 2, "0") + ":" + LPAD(TEXT(MINUTE(TIMEVALUE(CreatedDate + (1/24)))), 2, "0") + ":" + LPAD(TEXT(SECOND(TIMEVALUE(CreatedDate + (1/24)))), 2, "0")
CustomField.label: TSULTMOD
